Text: Thursday Nov American Red Cross blood driveup your iron to donate your Gift of Life The American Red Cross bloodmobile will be here Thursday November There are a few choice times available plus a drawing for Lancer tickets Call X for an appointment Elizabeth A Jones Health Unit

Gait analysis clinicPeak Performance employee will conduct a gait analysis clinic on Tuesday December in the Fitness Center Your gait can be video taped while on the treadmill and recommendations made for proper shoes Shoes and apparel will also be on display from Peak Performance Runners and walkers are welcome to attend For more information call X the Health Unit Elizabeth Jones

Gait analysisanalysis clinic is today Times still available You may also just visit the clinic and talk to Mike from Peak Performance You may enter Fitness Center door or East hallway door Elizabeth X
